      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/feds-bowman-lays-out-ambitious-agenda-overhaul-ease-bank-oversight-2025-06-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储周五，美联储的新最高监管官员提出了重新审视和放松众多银行规则和监督政策的雄心勃勃的议程，她认为这变得繁重和不必要。]]></description>
